-_NARA_-_7719070.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f8/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_33-Mile_Roadhouse_Restaurant_-_NARA_-_7719070.jpg","cap":"Valley of the Eagles 33 Mile Roadhouse Restaurant","desc":"The 33-Mile Roadhouse along the Haines Highway is a small haven known for its specialty hamburgers. Fuel services are also available. Location: Location: Alaska Status: Public domain. Lori Stepansky","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_33-Mile_Roadhouse_Restaurant_-_NARA_-_7719070.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/11/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Anway_House_-_NARA_-_7719072.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/11/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Anway_House_-_NARA_-_7719072.jpg","cap":"Valley of the Eagles Anway House","desc":"In this vintage photo, founder and owner Charles Anway stands by his home, today known as the Anway Homestead House. Location: Location: Alaska Status: Public domain. Courtesy of Sheldon Museum","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Anway_House_-_NARA_-_7719072.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/56/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Approaching_Porcupine_Crossing_in_Autumn_-_NARA_-_7719086.jpg/1280px-Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Approaching_Porcupine_Crossing_in_Autumn_-_NARA_-_7719086.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/56/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Approaching_Porcupine_Crossing_in_Autumn_-_NARA_-_7719086.jpg","cap":"Valley of the Eagles Approaching Porcupine Crossing in Autumn","desc":"Haines Highway bei Mosquito Lake; Abzweig zur Porcupine Bridge über den Klehini River nach Covenant Life CDP","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Approaching_Porcupine_Crossing_in_Autumn_-_NARA_-_7719086.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Approaching_the_Kluktoo_Slide_Area_-_NARA_-_7719082.jpg/1280px-Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Approaching_the_Kluktoo_Slide_Area_-_NARA_-_7719082.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/77/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Approaching_the_Kluktoo_Slide_Area_-_NARA_-_7719082.jpg","cap":"Valley of the Eagles Approaching the Kluktoo Slide Area","desc":"The northbound Haines Highway approaches the area of an old slide which devastated the Tlingit village of Kluktoo. Location: Location: Kluktoo, Alaska Status: Public domain. Lori Stepansky","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Approaching_the_Kluktoo_Slide_Area_-_NARA_-_7719082.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fc/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Council_Grounds_-_NARA_-_7719079.jpg/1280px-Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Council_Grounds_-_NARA_-_7719079.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fc/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Council_Grounds_-_NARA_-_7719079.jpg","cap":"Valley of the Eagles Council Grounds","desc":"The Council Grounds informational pullout has information kiosks where visitors can learn more about the Alaska Chilkat Bald Eagle Preserve. Location: Location: Alaska Chilkat Bald Eagle Preserve, Alaska Status: Public domain. Lori Stepansky","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Council_Grounds_-_NARA_-_7719079.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d6/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Haines_Highway--Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_NARA_-_7719078.jpg/1280px-Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Haines_Highway--Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_NARA_-_7719078.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d6/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Haines_Highway--Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_NARA_-_7719078.jpg","cap":"Valley of the Eagles Valley of the Eagles","desc":"At Mile Point 32, the driver sees the road heading directly north with the mountains of Alaska and Canada on the horizon and catches his or her breath knowing the only connection between them and this untouched, natural setting is the Haines Highway itself. Location: Location: Alaska (59.412° N 135.945° W) Status: Public domain. Lori Stepansky","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Haines_Highway--Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_NARA_-_7719078.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e1/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Interpretive_Signage_at_North_Council_Grounds_Pull-out_-_NARA_-_7719085.jpg/1280px-Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Interpretive_Signage_at_North_Council_Grounds_Pull-out_-_NARA_-_7719085.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e1/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Interpretive_Signage_at_North_Council_Grounds_Pull-out_-_NARA_-_7719085.jpg","cap":"Valley of the Eagles Interpretive Signage at North Council Grounds Pul","desc":"Interpretive panels about eagles stand under shelters at North Council Grounds, where visitors can see views of the river valley. Location: Location: North Council Grounds, Alaska Status: Public domain. Lori Stepansky","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Interpretive_Signage_at_North_Council_Grounds_Pull-out_-_NARA_-_7719085.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d4/Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Klehini_River_Scenic_Viewing_Area_-_NARA_-_7719084.jpg/1280px-Haines_Highway_-_Valley_of_the_Eagles_-_Klehini_River_Scenic_Viewing_Area_-_NARA_-_7